<para id="element-19">
An acceleration in downward direction means :
</para>
<para id="element-20">
(i)	lift is moving down with increasing speed
</para>
<para id="element-21">
(ii) lift is moving up with decreasing speed 
</para>
<para id="element-22">
Hence, options (b) and (c) are correct.
</para>
</solution>
</exercise>
</para>

